4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Course that aims to turn students into web development experts. The course covers building applications from scratch and provides the skills needed to become a successful Full-Stack Developer. The program lasts for 16+2 weeks, with 3 classes held weekly. Upon completion, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. No previous coding skills or advanced math knowledge are required. The course is available in both English and Spanish, and live classes are taught in the language of the student's campus. The program includes hands-on experience through the development and presentation of a personal project. More information can be found on their [website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop